  "detailed_description": "Battle Ball is a goofy multiplayer game about dodgeball, with more explosions and fewer rules. The goal in Battle Ball is to knock as many opponents out as you can in under 3 minutes. Team up with friends or join random players! <br><br>Don't have any friends? No problem! With version 1.1 Battle Ball now has a single-player mode where you can battle bots.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/3d86ce20cb46eafedcdc91cc809322d6.poster.avif?t=1620603622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/3d86ce20cb46eafedcdc91cc809322d6.webm?t=1620603622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/3d86ce20cb46eafedcdc91cc809322d6.mp4?t=1620603622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Express Yourself</h2>Earn Dodgebucks by playing in matches to spice up your look with crazy hats and outfits<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/5f3a4eb987cb73e46459a05d1cb978d5.poster.avif?t=1620603622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/5f3a4eb987cb73e46459a05d1cb978d5.webm?t=1620603622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514660/extras/5f3a4eb987cb73e46459a05d1cb978d5.mp4?t=1620603622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Dev</h2>Dad Hat Games is an independent studio, currently consisting of one member, who is passionate about creating fun experiences and looking forward to creating more projects",
